➜伯明汉青少儿英语告诉你，“网红”的英文该怎么说呢?
http://www.sohu.com/a/412776115_100197508	31798
<p class="ql-align-justify"> 信息大洪流时代，你的注意力被谁吸引了？网红们驻扎在上面紧紧的抓着流量，那么网红用英语又该怎么说呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> <strong>"网络红人"</strong>是指在现实或者网络生活中因为某个事件或者某个行为而被网民关注从而走红的人或长期持续输出专业知识而从红的人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200812/5b6b97cd5d4543088b7f150492c71e1a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> 那么，你知道怎么用<strong>英语更地道地表达“网红”</strong>吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> <strong>Wikipedia</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> An Internet celebrity, blogebrity, cyberstar, or online celebrity is someone who has become famous by means of the Internet. Internet allows people to reach a narrow audience across the world and so become famous within one or more Internet communities.</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> 上述中的Internet celebrity、blogebrity、cyberstar、online celebrity都可以用来表示网红哦！还可以说“Web Sensation” 。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> eg：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> He is a popular<strong> blogebrity</strong>.</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> 他是一个很受欢迎的网红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> <strong>an overnight sensation</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> 一夜成名的人（或事物）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> <strong>网红：Internet celebrity / blogebrity / cyberstar / online celebrity / Web Sensation</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
